{"blocks":[{"value":{"height":"200","url":"\/-content\/icing\/icon_256x256@2x.png?v=2","width":"200","description":"Icing icon"},"typeGroup":"media","type":"externalImage","identifier":"i-5246262939181179"},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"heading","identifier":"i-4270160160958767","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-9977706880308688","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Icing"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-4679662596900016","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-915919782128185","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Icing lets you create content: articles, blog posts, or about pages. It is available now to use online, and soon as a dedicated app for the Mac."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"subhead1","identifier":"i-6641330854035914","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-2208489398472011","type":"text","traits":{"link":{"typeChoice":{"URL":{"URL":"\/icing\/use\/"}}},"class":{"classNames":"primaryLink"}},"text":"Use Online for Free"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"subhead1","identifier":"i-19094125810079277","textItems":[{"text":"Benefits: no more markup","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-5909153346437961"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-23746242513880134","textItems":[{"text":"Icing doesn’t require a language like HTML or Markdown to be learned. ","type":"text","traits":{"bold":false},"identifier":"i-7970702068414539"},{"text":"Both have their strengths, however I think even Markdown can be little confusing to learn.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-9739535960834473"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-6639284810516983","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-41904707811772823","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Icing lets you make content that is flexible, using little pieces of text all strung together. "},{"identifier":"i-761142329312861","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Each piece can have "},{"identifier":"i-07667220290750265","type":"text","traits":{"italic":true},"text":"traits"},{"identifier":"i-7191298599354923","type":"text","traits":{},"text":", like whether the text is bold or italic, or if it has a link. "},{"identifier":"i-54328050930053","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Pretty much any small bit of info can be attached to a piece of text."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-9079991125036031","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-5026467037387192","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Apps like Microsoft Word or WordPress can be referred to by the strange term "},{"identifier":"i-7725950300227851","type":"text","traits":{"italic":true},"text":"What You See Is What You Get"},{"identifier":"i-8787055315915495","type":"text","traits":{},"text":". "},{"identifier":"i-81524349283427","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"The only problem with this is you often get only basic visual formatting, or if you want to do something more elaborate you either have to delve into HTML or are stuck unable to make what you like."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-22890478116460145","textItems":[{"text":"Icing has a rich structure like HTML whilst being much easier to use. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-5823140202555805"},{"text":"Structure is important, as it allows things to look and work consistently across all your content. Ideally it lets you put together exactly what you want without wrestling with your tools or having to rely on experts to do it for you.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-8987095693591982"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-05566198076121509","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-02222501370124519","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"You could call it a "},{"identifier":"i-08217177493497729","type":"text","traits":{"link":{"typeChoice":{"URL":{"URL":"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/WYSIWYM"}}},"italic":true},"text":"What You See Is What You Mean"},{"identifier":"i-835288678528741","type":"text","traits":{},"text":" editor if you wanted a strange name for it too."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"subhead1","identifier":"i-4879119119141251","textItems":[{"text":"Libraries","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-6807960907462984"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-3317005673889071","textItems":[{"text":"Let experts create libraries which have the different traits and elements that you need, and then put it together yourself. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-09613002114929259"},{"text":"Break a web page into distinct sections, each which can be set up in their own way:","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-33897631149739027"},{"text":"this is the main article, this is the introduction, this is a gallery.","type":"text","traits":{"italic":true},"identifier":"i-8524405816569924"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-48804869945161045","textItems":[{"text":"The content can be served on a website as is, or fully customised by a web developer. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-09929817775264382"},{"text":"Web developers can add whatever HTML attributes or CSS classes or JavaScript interactivity they like. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-2580025880597532"},{"text":"The best thing is the writer doesn’t have to worry themselves with those technicalities.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-368241484509781"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-40728264581412077","textItems":[{"text":"These transformations that developers set up can be packaged up into little libraries and shared, letting them be reused by anyone.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-3528024002443999"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-7304728727322072","textItems":[{"text":"A library could display a image slider, or show a summary of multiple items, or put footnotes at the bottom of the page, or add additional elements and attributes for better accessibility, or visibly show a link for printing, or create an RSS feed.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-8897781488485634"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"subhead1","identifier":"i-7046974536497146","textItems":[{"text":"The potential uses of Icing for writers, developers, and editors","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-9399827695451677"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","identifier":"i-5981560316868126","typeGroup":"subsection"},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-4425064269453287","textItems":[{"text":"Custom types: create new text types, or use ‘particular’ \/ ‘media’ blocks with fields to make customisable additions.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-03929480677470565"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-8976806767750531","textItems":[{"text":"Create static web pages: publish as flat HTML pages for speedy loading.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-11191598908044398"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-5510651194490492","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-22079027956351638","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Keep the basic content simple while allowing more advanced interactive elements to be externally interweaved. Allow typos to be corrected, additions to be included, customisations easily made by anyone without developer assistance."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-5236130675766617","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-8167669265531003","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Make multiple elements consistent while keeping their presentation (arrangement, formatting, punctuation) separate."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-5853690677322447","textItems":[{"text":"HTML agnostic: Isn’t directly connected to HTML, so alternate methods of publishing are possible: RSS, SVG, plain text, Markdown, ebook, PDF. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-7767849166411906"},{"text":"Icing documents are JSON, so create whatever transformations you like.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-7054212964139879"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-04064334533177316","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-5334390681236982","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"A simple format to convert into: hopefully to come will be tools to use Word, Excel, CSV, JSON and other file formats with Icing. This then could be published in the above formats, or dynamically processed in other ways."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-8566969146486372","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-9940420167986304","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Publish precisely by conforming formatting and structure: ideal for picky editors and web developers."}]}]}